Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,两线重合一公里左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个弯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,过了这个弯 就和东都线并行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的人影是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,人在紧急停车带里 旁边却没有汽车或摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,手里好像还拿着什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 停车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是炸弹 隧道里有炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,炸炸炸弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要到下个停车带才能停车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,起爆装置已经开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是目暮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是工藤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请立刻让列车停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹要炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,地铁跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是东都线列车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,工藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得前面有个弯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)\t(\fs100)}停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都知事 有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没事 谢谢
