Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过雪很软呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再滑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那几个孩子真快活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,带他们出来真是带对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,先不管那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小兰 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下 园子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别推我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么小兰和园子也来了…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的露天温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,梦寐以求的混浴露天温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等待我的是性感女士 还是娇美少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 水温刚刚好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样在旅途的蓝天下 边赏雪边泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是风雅啊 小姐
