Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.15,0:29:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.76,0:29:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.04,0:29:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.47,0:29:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才提到的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.98,0:29:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那就猫头鹰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.09,0:29:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说新一他…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.85,0:30:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好快 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.90,0:30:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都想试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.24,0:30:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,超赞的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.02,0:30:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.18,0:30:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,像坐过山车一样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.84,0:30:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好刺激啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.41,0:30:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.25,0:30:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 元太
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.49,0:30:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.92,0:30:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事 看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.76,0:30:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,元 元太
